{"name": "a vision of las californias  1", "description": "our home is both a place and a dream. a reality beyond nations where creativity runs wild and free. a vision of harmony across borders.

this tulengua collectible is many things at once - 
a visual.
a song.
and a one day ticket to our first ever binational festival. 

WELCOME TU LAS CALIFORNIAS 2022

november 4th and 5th
friday in tijuana, saturday in valle de guadalupe 

ft. tulengua, jazii, alec king, domino, joheel rodmar, unlucid juice, sarayu, kammari, and more tba.

FRIDAY: two stages of music + baja funk fashion + artisan crafts 
SATURDAY: intimate show + panel + private dinner + local wine 

this ticket is only for the FRIDAY show in tijuana. 
(saturday tickets sold separately). 

ps. this song - "every1" - was once the last song on our debut album, LOWKEYBANGERSVILLE, which no longer exists in its original form. 
we've decided to re-release this classic for the new internet.
we hope you enjoy. viva la musica.


3D lenguas by DIVERSO
